twitch_info.title: Kamilia III - Influka Area
twitch_info.description:
18 hours. 57 deaths to Kamilia's Balls.
Aimed > Walls > Arrows > Walls > Arrows
I found this fun but dying to moon in RNG-fest ways and seemingly not improving at the Balls phase felt bad. Although...I somehow pulled off not getting orbs at all and still won. Neat!
